    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example of BMW's high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual and a limited-slip differential, ensuring linear power delivery and exceptional mechanical feedback. Crucially, the chassis has undergone preventative subframe reinforcement and the rod bearings have been serviced to factory specifications. The exterior maintains its original factory luster with zero signs of oxidation, while the suspension geometry remains tight with refreshed bushings and dampers. This is a mechanically transparent, turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
