      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a showroom-quality vehicle that has been meticulously maintained since day one. This car is in absolute pristine condition, finished in a deep, glossy coat with zero imperfections\u2014no rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks to be found. It has been strictly garage-kept and hand-washed only. Inside, the cabin still carries that new-car aroma; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of wear, the carpets are spotless, and every electronic feature functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, it is flawless, backed by a comprehensive service history from certified technicians. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade example for a discerning buyer who demands perfection. Includes all original manuals, two sets of keys, and a clean title in hand.",
